  <div class="takeaways-content">
    <Fragment set:html={"<span class=\"takeaways-tag\">Love Your Neighbors</span>\n<h1 class=\"takeaways-title\">Dealing with Difficult People</h1>\n<p style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#7A7368;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:2.5rem;font-family:'EB Garamond',serif\">De-escalation phrases, correction techniques, and conflict frameworks</p>\n<div class=\"dd-topic-list\"><a class=\"dd-topic-link\" href=\"#dd-the-magic-de-escalators\">The Magic De-Escalators</a><a class=\"dd-topic-link\" href=\"#dd-giving-correction-without-offense\">Giving Correction Without Offense</a><a class=\"dd-topic-link\" href=\"#dd-initiating-healthy-conflict\">Initiating Healthy Conflict</a><a class=\"dd-topic-link\" href=\"#dd-appealing-to-nobler-motives\">Appealing to Nobler Motives</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"dd-category\" id=\"dd-the-magic-de-escalators\"><div class=\"dd-category-title\">The Magic De-Escalators</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">The Ultimate Empathy Phrase</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;I don&#x27;t blame you one iota for feeling as you do. If I were you I would undoubtedly feel just as you do.&quot;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">The Humble Inquiry</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;I may be wrong. I frequently am. And if I am right, I want to be corrected.&quot;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">The &#x27;Drop of Honey&#x27;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;I have respected the fact that you are always willing to listen and are big enough to change your mind when the facts warrant a change.&quot;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">Agree Quickly</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;Agree with thine adversary quickly.&quot;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dd-category\" id=\"dd-giving-correction-without-offense\"><div class=\"dd-category-title\">Giving Correction Without Offense</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">The &#x27;And&#x27; Method (Sandwich)</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Instead of using &#x27;but,&#x27; use &#x27;and.&#x27; Example: &quot;We&#x27;re really proud of you for raising your grades this term, and by continuing the same conscientious efforts next term, your algebra grade can be up with all the others.&quot;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">Admitting Your Own Faults First</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;You have made a mistake, but the Lord knows, it&#x27;s no worse than many I have made. I have been guilty of so many stupid, silly things myself...&quot;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">Asking Questions Instead of Orders</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;Do you think that would work?&quot; or &quot;Maybe if we were to phrase it this way it would be better?&quot;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">Indirect Correction</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Praise the specific behavior you want to see repeated (e.g., praising a messy worker for the one time they cleaned up).</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">Making the Fault Seem Easy to Correct</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;There is nothing to bridge except memory and judgment... Bridge will be a cinch for you.&quot;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dd-category\" id=\"dd-initiating-healthy-conflict\"><div class=\"dd-category-title\">Initiating Healthy Conflict</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">The Soft Opener</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;I feel like things aren&#x27;t right between us. Is there anything we should talk through?&quot;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">The Curiosity Approach</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;Assume the Best.&quot; Ask questions to understand their side rather than condemning.</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">The &#x27;Log in Eye&#x27; Check</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Before accusing, ask: &quot;Am I putting unfair expectations on this person to meet my needs?&quot;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">Seeking Reconciliation</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;Conflict is safe when you know you won&#x27;t quit each other.&quot;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dd-category\" id=\"dd-appealing-to-nobler-motives\"><div class=\"dd-category-title\">Appealing to Nobler Motives</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">The Reputation Play</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;I sized you up in the first place as being a man of your word... I&#x27;m willing to take a gamble.&quot;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">Giving a Fine Reputation to Live Up To</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;To show you I&#x27;m sure that you&#x27;ll never do this again, I want you to service my F-51 tomorrow.&quot;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">The Challenge</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">&quot;It&#x27;ll take a big person to go up there and stay.&quot;</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item-label\">Saving Face</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Let the other person save face; don&#x27;t just &quot;ram the unpalatable fact down our esophagus.&quot;</div>\n</div>"} />
  </div>

